### Get User by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/user/6918cdd5af071dfe25b6af83

### Create User
POST http://localhost:4000/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Johnson",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "address": {
    "street": "123 Main St",
    "city": "San Francisco",
    "zipCode": "94102",
    "country": "USA"
  },
  "preferences": {
    "newsletter": true,
    "notifications": "email"
  }
}

### Get User by Email
GET http://localhost:4000/user/email/alice@example.com

### Update User
PUT http://localhost:4000/user/6918cbbf157eccb436a8c022
